---
title: Spec‘Taco’lar Chicken Rice Bowls with Blue Corn Tortilla Chips, Pico de Gallo & Chili Lime Crema
description: For this taco-inspired meal, our chefs thought outside the tortilla—errr, box—to create some seriously epic rice bowls. They pile saucy spiced chicken and sautéed peppers and onions over buttery rice, then drizzle over a tangy chili lime crema and top with Monterey Jack cheese and homemade pico de gallo. On the side, the tortilla component comes in chip form for ultimate crunch-factor. Prepare to be totally bowled over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spectacolar-chicken-rice-bowls-4c48341b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spectacolar-chicken-rice-bowls-5fb7f4f52044c561a24f895e-c3286525.pdf
